(79, 'blog.element', '{\"has_image\":[\"1\"],\"title\":\"Best Online Pharmacy And Health Care Platform in Bangladesh\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"product-description__desc\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(68,65,65);font-family:Geologica, sans-serif;\\\">Medeasy provides affordable OTC (Over-the-Counter) medicines in Bangladesh. You\'ll find a wide range of over-the-counter medications and healthcare products to meet your various health and wellness needs. At Medeasy, we prioritize quality and safety. We source medicines from trusted manufacturers and suppliers to ensure that the OTC products we offer meet strict standards. Our commitment to excellence means you can be confident in the performance and reliability of the products you buy from us. We also offer women\'s healthcare products, dental care solutions, personal care solutions and diabetes care solutions.<\\/p><p class=\\\"product-description__desc\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:10px;margin-left:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(68,65,65);font-family:Geologica, sans-serif;\\\">At Medeasy Online Pharmacy BD, we are committed to your well-being and satisfaction. Our OTC category is designed to make it easy to find reliable and effective solutions for your everyday health concerns. Trust us to deliver quality products and exceptional service as you explore our diverse selection of over-the-counter medications and healthcare products.<\\/p><p class=\\\"product-description__desc\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:0px;margin-left:0px;padding:0px;font-size:16px;color:rgb(68,65,65);font-family:Geologica, sans-serif;\\\">Amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Maxime reprehenderit quaerat, velit rem atque vel impedit! Expensive Design.<\\/p>\",\"image\":\"66b9fb17861a21723464471.png\"}', '{\"image\":null,\"description\":null,\"social_title\":null,\"social_description\":null,\"keywords\":null}', 'basic', 'best-online-pharmacy-and-health-care-platform-in-bangladesh', '2024-08-12 06:07:51', '2024-08-12 06:07:54'),
(80, 'blog.element', '{\"has_image\":[\"1\"],\"title\":\"African Medicne : From Vision to Reality - Transforming Health Care for Millions\",\"description\":\"<p class=\\\"story-body-text\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0.75em;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.01);line-height:1.5;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', sans-serif;\\\">In a remote African village, imagine a woman\\u2013Nora\\u2013is pregnant with her first child. The nearest health center is hours away, but between prenatal visits, a community health worker checks in with her frequently to ensure the pregnancy progresses smoothly. Once Nora safely delivers her baby, the health worker continues to monitor mother and child, updating health records, including immunizations, using a digital platform that feeds information back into a national health data system. When supplies required by mothers, babies and other community members are low, medical drones quickly deliver the necessary products based on the data inputted by health workers.<\\/p><p class=\\\"story-body-text\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0.75em;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.01);line-height:1.5;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', sans-serif;\\\">This vision is a strong primary health care (PHC) system in action, capable of delivering\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.uhc2030.org\\/what-we-do\\/voices\\/action-agenda-from-the-uhc-movement\\/#:~:text=Ninety%20per%20cent%20of%20essential,recover%20from%20shocks%20and%20crises.\\\" class=\\\"external external-icon\\\" title=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.uhc2030.org\\/what-we-do\\/voices\\/action-agenda-from-the-uhc-movement\\/#:~:text=Ninety%20per%20cent%20of%20essential,recover%20from%20shocks%20and%20crises.\\\" style=\\\"background:0px 0px;color:rgb(16,87,159);margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\\\">90% of vital interventions<\\/a>\\u00a0required for universal health coverage. Unfortunately it is not yet a reality for many, but with strong political will, progressive health policies and strategic investment, it can be.<\\/p><p class=\\\"story-body-text\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0.75em;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.01);line-height:1.5;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', sans-serif;\\\"><br \\/><\\/p><p class=\\\"story-body-text\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0.75em;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.01);line-height:1.5;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', sans-serif;\\\">If we do it right, we can reimagine health care delivery in Africa and make essential health services available to the\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/ahaic.org\\/download\\/the-state-of-universal-health-coverage-in-africa\\/\\\" class=\\\"external external-icon\\\" title=\\\"https:\\/\\/ahaic.org\\/download\\/the-state-of-universal-health-coverage-in-africa\\/\\\" style=\\\"background:0px 0px;color:rgb(16,87,159);margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\\\">hundreds of millions<\\/a>\\u00a0of people across the continent who still lack access today, ensuring present and future generations have a better shot at living healthier, more prosperous lives.<\\/p><p class=\\\"story-body-text\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0.75em;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.01);line-height:1.5;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', sans-serif;\\\">The time to act has never been more critical. Global health goals are\\u00a0<a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/apnews.com\\/article\\/un-goals-report-poverty-gender-peace-climate-48d5b4e8833bce1b58191fe84bc6c22f\\\" class=\\\"external external-icon\\\" title=\\\"https:\\/\\/apnews.com\\/article\\/un-goals-report-poverty-gender-peace-climate-48d5b4e8833bce1b58191fe84bc6c22f\\\" style=\\\"background:0px 0px;color:rgb(16,87,159);margin:0px;padding:0px;vertical-align:baseline;\\\">stalling<\\/a>, health inequities are widening and the increasing impacts of climate change risk setting back the tenuous progress that has been made.<\\/p><p class=\\\"story-body-text\\\" style=\\\"margin-right:0px;margin-bottom:0.75em;margin-left:0px;background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.01);line-height:1.5;font-size:15px;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', sans-serif;\\\">In the face of these challenges, current strategies need rethinking. Today, many countries take a \\u201cone-size-fits-all\\u201d approach that fails to deliver quality, timely health care that meets the needs and preferences of the hardest-to-reach communities. By shifting away from this approach and toward what we call \\u201cResponsive\\u201d PHC, we can create systems that prioritize the needs of communities to accelerate progress toward health for all.<\\/p><div style=\\\"margin:0px;padding:0px;border:0px;vertical-align:baseline;background-color:rgb(255,255,255);color:rgb(51,51,51);font-family:Arial, \'Liberation Sans\', sans-serif;font-size:13px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;white-space:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-decoration-style:initial;clear:both;\\\"><\\/div>\",\"image\":\"66ba0179d07dc1723466105.png\"}', '{\"image\":null,\"description\":null,\"social_title\":null,\"social_description\":null,\"keywords\":null}', 'basic', 'african-medicne-from-vision-to-reality-transforming-health-care-for-millions', '2024-08-12 06:35:05', '2024-08-12 06:35:08'),
